version_description: The simple chord progression of this song, without the use of a capo or different tunings.

This version does not use a Capo, and is easy to play for beginners who choose not to use barre chords, as well as more advanced guitar players who can use the barre chords to create a rockier sound. Basically, this allows for a lot more flexibility than the versions of these chords with a Capo.
